    schema:description "This project responds to concerns raised by Yalmay Yunupingu and other staff within the Yirrkala School Language Production Centre related to the unauthorised use of their materials and knowledge and other related Intellectual Property issues.  Issues related to the appropriation of Indigenous knowledges and Yolŋu resources developed by Yolŋu educators and partners have emerged over recent years, with Yolŋu knowledge holders concerned about the lack of Yolŋu governance determining how this knowledge is used, distributed and shared." ;
